name: TO DAY THE ANGEL IS SMILING
description: This angel is only a supposition, such as a helper, liaison, or it could be a messenger. The representative of gratitude and happiness is a smile. Pandemic is a blessing when viewed from the side of wisdom, because many new things have emerged and become opportunities for a group of communities like today. Yes, working from home is a lot of fun. Lots of family time and we are made aware of the importance of family time. Many consider money more important than time with loved ones.
